DZN TEST FRAMEWORK
==================

Try:
    make help

Many convenience targets are avialable, such as,

    make check-out/Component

    make code-out/Component
    make verify-out/Component
    make check-out/dir.project

    make update-out/Component

    make update-code-out/Component
    make update-verify-out/Component
    make update-out/dir.project

running

    make VERBOSE=debug

lists them all.

Run server:

    make -C .. run

Authenticate dzn client:

    make -C .. hello

Go:
  make

CHECKS
======

  * code

regression/*.dzn
   - single-component code+CSP verification files (argument*.dzn)

regression/adapters
   - old IRun-Adapter-Main based single-file dzn tests AlarmSystem, Choice, camera

regression/parse
   - wellformdness and parser checks

regression/systems
   - system components

regression/dataparam.project/
   - non-generic main

regression/glue.project/
   - ASD-Dezyne project

regression/injected.project/
   - non-generic main

regression/lego.project/
   - multi-file project [c, c++]

EXTERNAL PROJECTS
=================

regression/autocryocycle.project/
   - convert and glue project [c++]
